  "title": "Barista",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ability to brew Coffee, to do espresso extraction, latte art in a nice and beautiful way</li>\n  <li>To prepare and innovate all other drinks</li>\n  <li>Ability to build rapport with customers and to welcome and inform them about our beans and our products.</li>\n  <li>Cleaning and restocking work at the coffee section, and sanitizing equipment and utensils.</li>\n  <li>In charge of opening and closing shifts one certain days</li>\n  <li>To innovate and build a portfolio of beverage</li>\n  <li>To build the beverage menu and brand</li>\n  <li>To recruit and train new comers</li>\n  <li>Placing orders to suppliers</li>\n</ul>\n<p>JOB REQUIREMENTS-</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2 yrs of barista experience</li>\n  <li>Ability to build rapport with the customers</li>\n  <li>Ability to build the beverage business</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants pls reach out at christine@mintgroup.sg </p>\n<p>or call 9058 6211 </p>",
